send their public relations.

211
00:13:04,599 --> 00:13:07,639
On the one hand,
they will promote these bloggers.

212
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:10,999
On the other hand,
they will also donate to charity projects

213
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,479
