266
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:06,320
Does it matter?

267
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,760
Anyway, our purpose is the same.

268
00:16:09,880 --> 00:16:11,238
Isn't this relationship

269
00:16:11,239 --> 00:16:13,519
